README
======

The CLDC and JNI test suites aim to test the Cacao JVM compiled for the JavaME/CLDC configuration.

Compiling the test suites
-------------------------

> ./build.sh --with-cldc-jar=/path/to/cldc1.1.jar

Flags to disable building of the CLDC or the JNI test suite:
 --disable-cldc-testsuite
 --disable-jni-testsuite

To see the other available flags, type:
> ./build.sh --help

Running the test suites
------------------------

> ./start-testsuites.sh

